{"tid":511874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「TC Candler」公佈2017年世界百大美女，子瑜獲第3成亞洲最美","createTime":"2017-12-28T01:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T07:56:03.000Z","uid":60286,"like":13,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a76d1d6316ee73017570f0f621d132647fade217","tid":511874,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T01:54:47.000Z","msg":"美國電影網站「TC Candler」近日公佈2017全球百大美女榜，南韓大勢女團TWICE台灣成員子瑜晉陞到第3名，首度擊敗蟬聯2年冠軍的NANA，成為「亞洲最美」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/095233_4c43fa6ffcad1c5afb3331b03a98009e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F095233_4c43fa6ffcad1c5afb3331b03a98009e.jpg&h=a1fe69b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜擊敗NANA成為亞洲最美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/094754_cbdce528d441db6351a0084ae4717cbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F094754_cbdce528d441db6351a0084ae4717cbf.jpg&h=29039253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNANA@After School<br />\n<br />\n子瑜出道才2個月，就被選進2015百大美女榜第13名，去年更躍升至第8名，連續3年都進榜的她，這次更晉陞到第3名，首度打敗連續兩年奪冠的After School成員NANA，成為「亞洲最美」，NANA則是下滑至第5名。<br />\n<br />\n冠軍為19歲的美國女星莉扎索伯拉奧，亞軍則是16歲法國模特兒黛蘭布蘭多，其他上榜還有TWICE日本籍成員SANA，首次入選拿下第21名，大陸「4000年美女」鞠婧禕第8名，迪麗熱巴第26名，李聖經第32名，石原聰美第34名，「少女時代」太妍第40名，秀智第51名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/094822_67573d7ca76b71f1ce590a3a496fcc54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F094822_67573d7ca76b71f1ce590a3a496fcc54.jpg&h=09bdd04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太妍@少女時代<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/094833_1292eacfde119ba3a928df43c068bd37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F094833_1292eacfde119ba3a928df43c068bd37.jpg&h=811b87c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石原聰美<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/094855_343ad59f423fd7f699018319636fe656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F094855_343ad59f423fd7f699018319636fe656.jpg&h=6808f70d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGal Gadot<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/094918_b02d2b03d667b296c3c515f337ed06c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F094918_b02d2b03d667b296c3c515f337ed06c9.png&h=0e8823be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凱特（Kate Middleton)王妃<br />\n<br />\n比不少明星更有光芒的，是英國劍橋公爵夫人凱特王妃。她形像高貴大方，每次出席公眾場合，優雅打扮都令人眼前一亮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/095211_112f665954213a488148494ee6dade92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F095211_112f665954213a488148494ee6dade92.jpg&h=59168ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一名由19歲美國女星莉扎索伯拉奧奪下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Px_S0T4oOYo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPx_S0T4oOYo&d=Z4JEb5%2BBPZNdO12kQ4Fh1gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9670c962\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Px_S0T4oOYo</a>"},{"pid":"52cf7144ac3bd9ee978e00ffb8b74a8926e978d7","tid":511874,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:14:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8eb3dc401e899fd3306263c51425f535805dfb9c","tid":511874,"uid":93986,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"有冇肥婆上？<br />\n點解冇？<br />\n因為肥婆就是垃圾"},{"pid":"f3a59e490393d09d4faaafe2bbfcfb83e605d44f","tid":511874,"uid":28619,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"第1個個咁普通"},{"pid":"c4cc038e44537879030f4e55927ad804efda145f","tid":511874,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T0